CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1781633474
OL,3,CMan charged with multiple offences
OL,4,Cafter car hits bowling alley
OL,6,FIn a statement issued on social media,
OL,7,Fthey said: "Due to circumstances
OL,8,Fbeyond our control, we will be closed
OL,9,Funtil further notice. Please know we
OL,10,Fwill be back open once we're allowed!
OL,12,F"A huge thank you to all the emergency
OL,13,Fservices involved yesterday! We are
OL,14,Fextremely grateful those injured only
OL,15,Fsuffered minor injuries.
OL,17,F"Thank you all for the supportive
OL,18,Fcomments and love it means the world
OL,19,Fto the team!"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/3
